\" href=\"./Mathlib/NumberTheory/LucasLehmer.html#LucasLehmer.norm_num_ext.sModNatTR\"><span class=\"name\">LucasLehmer</span>.<span class=\"name\">norm_num_ext</span>.<span class=\"name\">sModNatTR</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">q </span><span class=\"fn\">k</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Tail-recursive version of `sModNat`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/NumberTheory/LucasLehmer.html#LucasLehmer.norm_num_ext.sModNatTR","kind":"def","line":658,"name":"LucasLehmer.norm_num_ext.sModNatTR","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/NumberTheory/LucasLehmer.lean#L658-L666"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/NumberTheory/LucasLehmer.html#LucasLehmer.norm_num_ext.sModNat_eq_sMod\"><span class=\"name\">LucasLehmer</span>.<span class=\"name\">norm_num_ext</span>.<span class=\"name\">sModNat_eq_sMod</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p </span><span class=\"fn\">k</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hp</span> : <span class=\"fn\">2</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LE.le\">≤</a> <span class=\"fn\">p</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/NumberTheory/LucasLehmer.html#LucasLehmer.norm_num_ext.sModNat\">sModNat</a> (<span class=\"fn\">2</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HPow.hPow\">^</a> <span class=\"fn\">p</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSub.hSub\">-</a> <span class=\"fn\">1</span>) <span class=\"fn\">k</span>)</span></span